I told you
I didn't want him to testify.

27:14.678 --> 27:16.342
We needed him.
He's our most crucial witness.

27:16.379 --> 27:18.113
I don't care.

27:18.910 --> 27:20.894
I didn't want to bring him into this.

27:20.996 --> 27:22.902
I never want to hurt anyone.

27:22.949 --> 27:24.062
This case is over.

27:24.099 --> 27:25.682
You're-you're fired.

27:30.605 --> 27:32.152
<i>ALDERS: With crime skyrocketing,</i>

27:32.189 --> 27:33.927
<i>we need now more than ever</i>

27:33.964 --> 27:36.389
<i>a law to protect the rights of victims.</i>

27:37.019 --> 27:40.777
<i>Rosemary's Law, named
after poor Rosemary Lynch,</i>

27:40.863 --> 27:44.074
<i>is the perfect law
for these imperfect times.</i>

27:44.501 --> 27:46.468
<i>Let's take a look.</i>

27:48.332 --> 27:50.146
You dragged me up two flights of stairs

27:50.183 --> 27:52.910
to watch this wretched woman
push your crap bill?

27:53.175 --> 27:55.060
I disagree, Senator.

27:55.199 --> 27:57.060
Chicago is getting pummeled
in the national media

27:57.097 --> 27:58.551
for excessive violence.

27:58.707 --> 28:01.449
And your self-serving law
does nothing to curb it.

28:01.612 --> 28:03.318
Look, we all know
you're trying to neutralize

28:03.355 --> 28:04.808
Madeline Scott's attacks on you.

28:04.845 --> 28:09.004
Who, at this very moment,
is trying to free

28:09.063 --> 28:12.381
the Jihadist Baby Killer from prison.

28:13.448 --> 28:15.198
I agree it's not a great look.

28:15.354 --> 28:17.521
But neither is having
this famous victim here

28:17.566 --> 28:19.138
to try to sway me.

28:21.100 --> 28:23.575
And if you don't vote
for Rosemary's Law,

28:23.612 --> 28:26.348
I'll come after you in the press
for being soft on crime.

28:26.925 --> 28:29.926
As a famous victim,
I bet there's plenty of voters

28:29.963 --> 28:32.014
interested in what I think
about this subject.

28:33.033 --> 28:35.620
Her anger and her disappointment

28:35.964 --> 28:38.409
might just force Isabel to...

28:39.019 --> 28:40.820
run against you in the primary.

28:41.167 --> 28:43.464
Hispanic. Beautiful.

28:43.592 --> 28:45.466
Intelligent.

28:46.246 --> 28:47.467
Seems like an excellent time

28:47.504 --> 28:49.204
to primary an old white guy.

28:49.387 --> 28:51.756
Since they're dropping
like flies in every primary

28:51.793 --> 28:53.541
- in the country.
- All right, all right.

28:53.801 --> 28:55.701
I'll take another look at it.

28:57.914 --> 28:59.949
I won't forget this one.

29:03.945 --> 29:06.554
Rosemary Lynch is never gonna go away.

29:07.093 --> 29:08.654
We have to use her to your advantage,

29:08.691 --> 29:11.492
or she's gonna hang over
your entire campaign.

29:12.023 --> 29:14.562
All I ever did was try to get
justice for that poor girl.

29:15.088 --> 29:17.072
And her parents.

29:18.465 --> 29:21.282
Now she's gonna haunt me to my grave.

