We've been working on this case, right?

30:03.878 --> 30:06.130
And there's this couple, and they...

30:07.050 --> 30:08.505
Well, they come
from different religions,

30:08.542 --> 30:09.990
so they keep their whole relationship

30:10.027 --> 30:11.510
a secret from everyone.

30:12.222 --> 30:13.932
And they love each other, but,

30:13.969 --> 30:17.746
keeping their relationship
a secret destroys it.

30:19.810 --> 30:21.768
Come on, Bodie.

30:22.300 --> 30:24.390
You knew what this was when we started.

30:24.556 --> 30:26.027
- Mm-hmm.
- Yeah.

30:26.183 --> 30:27.700
Let me ask you.

30:28.135 --> 30:29.810
Would you feel differently about us

30:29.847 --> 30:32.524
if my job wasn't getting
innocent people out of prison?

30:35.370 --> 30:36.860
Are they innocent?

30:36.897 --> 30:40.089
Is the Chicago PD never wrong?
They never make a mistake?

30:40.126 --> 30:42.635
- They're just all a bunch of saints?
- Well, some of us are.

30:42.772 --> 30:45.341
We're not the ones getting killers,

30:45.378 --> 30:47.419
rapists, drug dealers set free.

30:47.456 --> 30:49.176
People we risked our lives

30:49.213 --> 30:50.453
to put behind bars in the first place.

30:50.489 --> 30:52.310
No, I'm protecting the innocent. Okay?

30:52.347 --> 30:53.953
Unlike some cops, which, honestly,

30:53.990 --> 30:55.707
I think have a hard time
telling the difference.

30:55.882 --> 30:58.424
I'm out. We're done.

30:58.731 --> 31:00.239
[NIKKI SIGHS]

31:00.919 --> 31:02.503
Really?

31:03.056 --> 31:04.527
Yeah, really.

31:04.724 --> 31:06.057
God, you know...

31:06.175 --> 31:08.467
Whatever. I can't believe
I was so wound up on you.

31:08.562 --> 31:10.613
Yeah, right back at you.

31:12.260 --> 31:14.570
You were wound up about me?

31:17.636 --> 31:19.312
[DOOR OPENS]

31:19.708 --> 31:21.191
[DOOR CLOSES]

31:22.191 --> 31:24.465
I'm so sorry, Sarah.

31:24.714 --> 31:26.986
I know how much
you didn't want him there.

31:27.080 --> 31:29.378
But we desperately needed
his testimony.

31:29.594 --> 31:32.902
I have ruined his life once,

31:33.031 --> 31:34.275
and now I've done it again.

31:34.312 --> 31:37.330
All I do is hurt people.

31:37.589 --> 31:40.056
My parents. My community.

31:40.409 --> 31:42.485
My baby.

31:43.214 --> 31:44.912
I deserve this.

31:45.001 --> 31:48.294
I deserve everything
that has happened to me.

31:51.024 --> 31:52.574
Since you're not gonna kill yourself,

31:52.699 --> 31:54.458
why don't you figure out how
to get out of here?

31:54.724 --> 31:56.409
What are you talking about?

32:01.361 --> 32:03.245
Of course you don't.

32:04.105 --> 32:06.784
All you did is what
hundreds of millions of women

32:06.821 --> 32:08.763
have done for centuries.

32:09.253 --> 32:10.622
You got pregnant.

32:11.253 --> 32:13.433
You felt trapped and ashamed,

32:13.470 --> 32:15.273
and so you kept it a secret.

32:15.353 --> 32:18.191
What happened to you was a tragedy.

32:18.387 --> 32:20.912
You don't deserve any of this.

32:22.794 --> 32:24.402
Sarah.

32:25.292 --> 32:27.261
We're both people of faith.

32:28.183 --> 32:30.716
We love God,
and we want to follow His way.

32:31.613 --> 32:34.370
He is punishing me for what I did.

32:34.762 --> 32:36.912
Or-or was He testing you?

32:39.730 --> 32:42.328
Maybe He wants you to represent
your religion to a country

32:42.365 --> 32:44.378
that discriminates against it.

32:47.495 --> 32:49.483
Maybe He wants you
to be a symbol of freedom

32:49.520 --> 32:51.704
by fighting for your own.

32:53.344 --> 32:55.221
You really think so?

32:55.599 --> 32:57.657
I do.

32:58.472 --> 33:00.494
We have a saying in my religion.

33:01.331 --> 33:04.567
"The Lord works in mysterious ways."

33:05.558 --> 33:07.661
[CRYING]: We say <i> "Allahu A'lam."</i>

33:07.722 --> 33:08.964
[SNIFFLES]

33:09.086 --> 33:11.102
Which means "Allah knoweth."

33:11.339 --> 33:13.448
[SIGHS]

33:18.544 --> 33:20.206
Let us keep fighting.

33:22.179 --> 33:25.247
We're gonna get you out of here,
or we're gonna die trying.

33:27.276 --> 33:28.925
Okay.

33:29.707 --> 33:31.808
Let's keep fighting.

33:34.708 --> 33:36.690
I started to bleed.

33:37.089 --> 33:38.784
I was terrified because I...

33:38.821 --> 33:40.913
I didn't know what was happening.

33:41.519 --> 33:43.818
I went to the bathroom,
and the next thing I knew,

33:43.855 --> 33:45.124
I had delivered.

33:45.218 --> 33:47.093
I was shocked. I...

33:48.722 --> 33:52.114
I checked to see if the baby
was breathing, and it...

33:52.444 --> 33:54.053
it wasn't. It...

33:56.534 --> 33:58.896
Was the baby alive when you delivered?

33:59.152 --> 34:02.308
No. It wasn't.

34:05.707 --> 34:08.542
Why did you dispose of the fetus
the way you did?

34:09.706 --> 34:11.313
I was so, so scared.

34:11.368 --> 34:13.685
I didn't know what else to do.

34:15.663 --> 34:18.598
And I bet your baby was scared, too.

34:19.694 --> 34:21.956
Terrified from the pain.

34:28.802 --> 34:30.237
Janice.

34:30.418 --> 34:31.706
This is crazy.

34:31.743 --> 34:33.431
I know, but that's Bryant.

34:35.003 --> 34:36.675
How about we cut a deal?

34:36.752 --> 34:39.161
All right? She pleads guilty
to unlawful disposal of a fetus

34:39.188 --> 34:41.277
and gets out for time served.

34:42.358 --> 34:44.214
Come on. I know you want her out.

34:44.341 --> 34:47.168
If I do it, Bryant will hate me
till the end of time.

34:47.205 --> 34:48.636
And you'll go back to Cook County,

34:48.672 --> 34:50.356
and I'll still have to deal with him.

34:50.641 --> 34:52.190
I can't help you.

34:52.716 --> 34:54.650
[SIGHS]

35:03.046 --> 35:05.046
♪ ♪

35:32.583 --> 35:34.133
[LAUGHS]

35:34.997 --> 35:37.254
You sure this belt doesn't look stupid?

35:37.328 --> 35:38.828
No, it looks hot.

35:38.948 --> 35:40.410
[BOTH CHUCKLE]

35:42.060 --> 35:43.771
Thought all the ex-con bars were

35:43.808 --> 35:45.128
- on the other side of town.
- [CHUCKLES]

35:45.164 --> 35:47.155
Yeah, but I heard this is
a great place to score Adderall.

35:47.192 --> 35:48.770
You know where I can get some?

35:48.887 --> 35:50.416
- What?
- What was your father

35:50.453 --> 35:52.912
doing prescribing Adderall to Rosemary?

35:53.590 --> 35:55.870
I don't know anything about this.

35:57.122 --> 35:58.592
He didn't even know Rosemary.

35:58.629 --> 36:00.242
Now, why don't you just
leave us the hell alone?

36:00.317 --> 36:02.336
You know, nothing
would make me happier,

36:02.434 --> 36:05.176
but your wife keeps
popping back into my life.

36:05.403 --> 36:08.526
And right when I started
investigating Rosemary's murder.

36:09.254 --> 36:11.028
Why do you think that is?

36:11.465 --> 36:14.590
I'll tell you exactly how
you can find Rosemary's killer.

36:15.328 --> 36:16.872
How?

36:17.686 --> 36:19.762
- Just look in the mirror.
- [CHUCKLES]

36:19.992 --> 36:21.992
Come on, Brian.

36:23.331 --> 36:25.665
It's not the belt that's stupid.

36:28.278 --> 36:29.764
