36:37.161 --> 36:38.778
♪ <i>Sockets feeling tired</i> ♪

36:38.841 --> 36:40.598
♪ <i>Spiral down the calendar</i> ♪

36:40.642 --> 36:43.217
♪ <i>A rocket in the fire...</i> ♪

36:44.048 --> 36:46.024
NIKKI: License and registration.

36:46.457 --> 36:48.516
[GARBLED RADIO TRANSMISSION]

36:50.368 --> 36:52.614
What are you stopping me for, Officer?

36:54.190 --> 36:56.524
For being a very bad boy.

36:59.933 --> 37:02.951
Well, maybe I need to be spanked.

37:03.204 --> 37:05.187
I'll let you off with a warning.

37:07.372 --> 37:08.882
And if you want to keep getting off,

37:08.919 --> 37:11.333
you should come
to my apartment... right now.

37:11.509 --> 37:13.175
Of course, Officer.

37:13.567 --> 37:15.926
I always follow the law.

37:21.759 --> 37:23.993
Somebody missed me.

37:24.340 --> 37:26.906
♪ <i>Dangerous</i> ♪

37:26.943 --> 37:29.828
♪ <i>To live like us...</i> ♪

37:30.059 --> 37:32.652
[OVERLAPPING SHOUTING]

37:35.314 --> 37:37.189
Keep back.

37:37.392 --> 37:39.858
<i>MADELINE:
Shame by itself is not a crime.</i>

37:40.041 --> 37:41.935
But shame is the issue here.

37:42.916 --> 37:45.918
The shame of a young woman,
barely past her teen years,

37:45.955 --> 37:48.701
who felt she had to hide her pregnancy.

37:49.088 --> 37:53.322
The shame of deciding whether to
keep a baby she might not want.

37:54.041 --> 37:56.208
The shame of hiding the identity

37:56.245 --> 38:00.345
of that baby's father to protect <i> him.</i>

38:01.419 --> 38:03.794
Sarah Bukhari made mistakes.

38:04.713 --> 38:08.408
And for those mistakes, she had
her whole life taken from her.

38:08.744 --> 38:12.129
She's being used as a tool
for political advocates

38:12.166 --> 38:14.838
to punish women for having an abortion.

38:14.890 --> 38:17.666
When the sad irony is
she didn't even have one.

38:17.787 --> 38:19.611
[GALLERY MURMURING]

38:19.685 --> 38:23.578
If protecting life
is the goal of the State,

38:24.009 --> 38:26.978
why aren't we protecting
a woman's life as well?

38:28.439 --> 38:30.684
Denying Sarah her freedom

38:31.213 --> 38:33.808
would not only be a lost opportunity

38:33.845 --> 38:36.814
at righting a great wrong.

38:37.235 --> 38:41.025
It would place
the greatest shame upon us all.

38:44.649 --> 38:46.616
Ms. Scott...

38:48.021 --> 38:51.096
...that was a moving closing argument,

38:51.517 --> 38:53.916
but I have a different view,

38:54.095 --> 38:57.603
and that is all life is precious.

38:58.220 --> 39:00.722
Terminated pregnancies
are seen as murder

39:00.759 --> 39:03.603
to tens of millions
of people in this country.

39:03.786 --> 39:07.687
Murder of a life that has
no means of defending itself.

39:08.361 --> 39:10.449
When a woman gets pregnant,

39:10.567 --> 39:14.378
she becomes God's partner in creation.

39:14.916 --> 39:17.572
Whether your client had an abortion

39:17.791 --> 39:20.051
or simply failed to see a doctor...

39:20.169 --> 39:23.322
which she admits she did not...

39:23.658 --> 39:26.265
she did not protect that life.

39:27.759 --> 39:30.561
Maybe she was filled with shame.

39:30.994 --> 39:32.563
But a greater shame is

39:32.614 --> 39:35.955
her unborn child never even
stood a fair chance.

39:37.253 --> 39:39.838
Therefore I am denying
your motion for a new trial.

39:39.931 --> 39:42.648
[GALLERY MURMURING]

39:43.267 --> 39:45.580
Your Honor, the State has agreed
to allow the petitioner

39:45.617 --> 39:48.441
to plead guilty
to unlawful disposal of a fetus,

39:48.478 --> 39:51.181
and requests she be released
immediately for time served.

39:51.291 --> 39:52.627
Now, you listen to me, little lady...

39:52.664 --> 39:54.041
The petitioner's evidentiary showing

39:54.078 --> 39:55.762
throughout these proceedings
has led the State

39:55.799 --> 39:58.087
to believe the defendant
has served her time.

39:58.189 --> 40:00.541
MADELINE: And if the State
rejects this plea offer,

40:00.720 --> 40:02.927
I'll appeal this all the way
to the Supreme Court.

40:03.494 --> 40:05.470
I'll never go away, Your Honor.

40:05.767 --> 40:08.595
[SIGHS] That I don't find
hard to believe.

40:08.706 --> 40:10.134
And in the future, I would appreciate

40:10.171 --> 40:13.110
if the court referred to me
as Deputy Prosecutor Molina

40:13.147 --> 40:14.997
or just Deputy Prosecutor.

40:15.705 --> 40:18.775
That's fine, Deputy Prosecutor,

40:18.886 --> 40:21.795
and I look forward
to seeing you again in my court.

40:22.676 --> 40:24.705
As do I, Your Honor.

40:28.158 --> 40:31.363
Defendant is released based on
the plea deal and time served.

40:31.400 --> 40:32.962
May the Lord save her soul.

40:33.016 --> 40:37.092
- [GALLERY CLAMORING]
- [CHEERING]

40:37.681 --> 40:40.072
So, I'm really free?

40:40.205 --> 40:42.133
- Mm-hmm.
- [EXHALES]

40:42.258 --> 40:44.158
[CRYING]

40:44.603 --> 40:47.954
[GALLERY CLAMORING]

40:48.291 --> 40:49.974
Thank you.

40:50.357 --> 40:52.658
You hold your head up.

40:53.802 --> 40:55.835
<i>VIOLET: The worst part about shame</i>

40:55.938 --> 40:58.653
<i>is how it eats away at our souls.</i>

40:58.842 --> 41:02.469
It convinces us that we are
the worst version of ourselves

41:02.525 --> 41:04.212
and destroys our hope

41:04.257 --> 41:07.533
that we'll ever find true peace.

41:09.532 --> 41:11.657
♪ <i>So bring what you got</i> ♪

41:11.787 --> 41:13.845
♪ <i>Bring it now</i> ♪

41:14.083 --> 41:16.650
♪ <i>You can't knock me down</i> ♪

41:16.727 --> 41:18.894
- ♪ <i>Oh, oh</i> ♪ - ♪ <i>Can't knock me down</i> ♪

41:19.155 --> 41:21.447
- ♪ <i>Oh, oh, oh...</i> ♪ - [DOOR OPENS]

41:22.699 --> 41:24.082
Wow.

41:24.201 --> 41:25.918
You look good.

41:26.166 --> 41:28.253
I'm sorry I haven't
been here in a while.

41:28.347 --> 41:31.986
It's cool. If I were you, I
wouldn't come back here either.

41:32.108 --> 41:33.566
I missed you.

41:33.728 --> 41:35.572
I think about you a lot.

41:35.913 --> 41:38.747
Is that why you came back? To see me?

41:39.398 --> 41:41.382
Mm-hmm.

41:42.361 --> 41:43.752
And I feel ashamed

41:43.789 --> 41:45.692
that I haven't visited you in so long.

41:45.746 --> 41:49.006
Ah, I just figured
you were seeing someone new.

41:49.043 --> 41:50.576
There's a guy.

41:50.613 --> 41:52.538
A guy? [CHUCKLES]

41:53.228 --> 41:54.627
I'm not surprised.

41:54.712 --> 41:56.462
- [CLEARS THROAT]
- You like him?

41:57.384 --> 41:58.698
I do.

41:59.197 --> 42:00.936
So, what do you want... my permission?

42:01.535 --> 42:02.663
You don't me owe anything.

42:02.700 --> 42:04.621
You know, we had a thing,
but it's cool.

42:04.658 --> 42:05.939
Uh, it was more than a thing.

42:05.976 --> 42:07.801
You were the first love of my life.

42:09.118 --> 42:10.893
It was all right.

42:13.924 --> 42:15.657
You love him?

42:16.062 --> 42:17.400
[CHUCKLES] No.

42:17.437 --> 42:20.386
It's way too early for all that.
[CLEARS THROAT]

42:20.423 --> 42:22.750
Mainly, I just feel stupid
around him all the time.

42:23.051 --> 42:24.442
What do you mean?

42:24.595 --> 42:26.148
I don't know. I'm always a...

42:26.728 --> 42:28.705
afraid I'm gonna say the wrong thing,

42:28.802 --> 42:30.444
laugh at the wrong time.

42:30.818 --> 42:33.150
I don't know how
to be myself around him.

42:33.396 --> 42:35.361
Never did this before.

42:37.774 --> 42:40.584
WREN: Just relax.
Don't think about it too much.

42:41.930 --> 42:43.791
He's a guy. He probably
doesn't notice anyway.

42:43.853 --> 42:46.433
[BOTH LAUGH]

42:50.370 --> 42:52.646
It was never awkward with us.

42:54.129 --> 42:56.363
We spent a long time together.

42:58.345 --> 43:00.813
